                "img": "派蒙-4",
                "pos": "left",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447711-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "迪希雅？你怎么突然不说话了…",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-2",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447712-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "…啊，抱歉，想起了一些过去的事情。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "paimon",
                "img": "派蒙-4",
                "pos": "left",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447713-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "过去？迪希雅以前过生日也会买很多漂亮的饰品吗？",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447714-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "不，沙漠中并没有这么多新奇的玩意儿。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447715-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "不过在我小的时候，有一次生日，库塞拉…我的老爹，他用一些不知从哪弄来的奇怪装扮，把我从头到脚打扮了一番。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447716-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "大家把我围在中间，唱着不成调的曲子。然后老爹端来加了满满一碗枣椰肉的牛奶，让我对着它许个生日愿望。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "player",
                "img": "aether3",
                "pos": "left",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447717-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "你父亲很用心。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447718-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "是吗？老爹总是笨手笨脚的，他套在我脚上的鞋大了好几码，每走一步就会灌一脚沙子。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d447719-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "还有那碗牛奶，因为加了太多枣椰肉，甜到有些发腻。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d44771a-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "呵呵…很滑稽吧？现在回想起来，佣兵团里都是些粗鲁的汉子，老爹肯定也不知道该如何给女儿过一个理想的生日吧。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "player",
                "img": "aether2",
                "pos": "left",
                "key": "gal-line-2d44771b-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "迪希雅…",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-2",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d449e20-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "哈哈哈，别露出那样的表情啊。现在不是还有你们陪着我嘛。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d449e21-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "能像今天这样和朋友一起庆祝的生日，于我而言来之不易。",
                "ext": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "simple_dialog",
                "chara": "deheya",
                "img": "迪希雅-1",
                "pos": "right",
                "key": "gal-line-2d449e22-d42a-11ed-9ed0-9f29bdbc63a6",
                "content": "所以，谢谢你们今天过来陪我。",
                "ext": ""
            }
        ]
    }
